java.io.Serializable, ModelIdentifier, ObrModelIdentifier
public class ObrCompositeModelIdentifierImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ObrModelIdentifier

Composite Model Identifier. Contains a main Id and a secondary Id. The main Id is used in getDOID to return the internal OBR ID The seconday Id is used to store the ObrModelIdentifier (a composite too) of the parent. This will define uniquely the whole hierarchy for a FactProperty. Note : this class is generic and can be used in another context than the example above.
